data.description: Welcome Home!  Adorable home with three bedrooms upstairs with two full bathrooms. Located just minutes from beautiful Lake Livingston.  Downstairs room can be used as a primary bedroom - complete with full bath- an office or dining room. You have several options how you can use this large space!  Home has a brand new roof and central ac& heat.  There are new laminate floors, fresh paint and new interior doors throughout.  Kitchen has new cabinetry and countertops with natural gas!  There is a large pantry and laundry room off the kitchen.  Back yard is fully fenced and complete with an RV hookup.  Step out the french doors onto your beautiful covered deck!  This home has so much to offer. Schedule your showing today -This one will not last!
